      things would move fast when working with Tfue – a household name-level
      streamer – who made plans with us on the fly with little structure or time
      to develop ideas.
    </p>
    <p>
      Driving a narrative through multiple events, keeping fans engaged with a
      series that was flashy, high-stakes, and ever-present, generating buzz and
      engagement around when the next entry would take place.
