<div>
  <h2>Creative Approach</h2>

  <div class="side-by-side">
    <p class="big">Inspiration from the Classics</p>
    <p>
      Drawing inspiration from the most iconic medium for ongoing narratives –
      comic books – the name Tfue Tuesday took shape as a catchy title for an
      event series that could span multiple volumes, like how comics release
      over multiple issues. The aesthetic translated seamlessly across broadcast
      graphics, trailers, and promotional assets, reinforcing the tournament’s
      legendary, high-stakes atmosphere.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

