<div class="side-by-side">
  <p class="big">Turning Tfue’s Return Into a Cinematic Event</p>
  <p>
    After taking an extended hiatus from the streaming world, Tfue returned to
    the spotlight with the third installation of Tfue Tuesday, just in time for
    Fortnite's OG event. I aimed to craft a trailer that evoked a melodramatic
    comic book storyline - framing the story around his dramatic exit from the
    streaming world, and triumphant return. For Vol. 3, Tfue's return became a
    significant part of the storyline, making the event feel like a cultural
    moment in competitive Fortnite.
  </p>
</div>

